Subject: dorsal region of the whole animal [PLANA:0000141]
Value: Three dimensional compartment along the dorsoventral axis that is above the anteroposterior axis,  containing the eyes.

Subject: dorsal compartment [PLANA:0007504]
Value: Three dimensional compartment along the dorsoventral axis that is above the anteroposterior axis,  containing the eyes.

Subject: posterior compartment of the whole animal [PLANA:0000142]
Value: Three dimensional compartment along the anteroposterior axis that is closer to the tail rather than the head, from the anterior boundary of the pharyngeal pouch to the tip of the tail.

Subject: posterior compartment [PLANA:0007507]
Value: Three dimensional compartment along the anteroposterior axis that is closer to the tail rather than the head, from the anterior boundary of the pharyngeal pouch to the tip of the tail.

Subject: ventral compartment of the whole animal [PLANA:0000143]
Value: Compartment along the dorsoventral axis that is below the anteroposterior axis.

Subject: ventral compartment [PLANA:0007505]
Value: Compartment along the dorsoventral axis that is below the anteroposterior axis.

Subject: anterior region of the whole animal [PLANA:0000140]
Value: Compartment along the anteroposterior axis closer to the head rather than the tail, from the head margin to the esophagus.

Subject: anterior compartment [PLANA:0007506]
Value: Compartment along the anteroposterior axis closer to the head rather than the tail, from the head margin to the esophagus.

Subject: ventral epidermis [PLANA:0000096]
Value: ventral region of the epidermal compartment

Subject: definitive pharynx progenitor [PLANA:0000110]
Value: foxA1+ neoblasts and their post-mitotic, differentiating daughters required for maintenance and regeneration of the definitive pharynx.

Subject: circular muscle progenitor cell [PLANA:0000130]
Value: piwi-1+, nkx1-1+ progenitor neoblasts required for specification of circular muscle fibers.

Subject: longitudinal muscle progenitor cell [PLANA:0000134]
Value: piwi-1+, myoD+, snail-1+ progenitor neoblasts required for specification and creation of longitudinal muscle fibers.

Subject: male germline stem cell [PLANA:0000219]
Value: gh4+, nanos+ cells residing at the testis periphery that self-renew and give rise to differentiating daughters that will ultimately produce haploid sperm.

Subject: germ cell [PLANA:0000227]
Value: 1. A gamete (as an egg or sperm cell) or one of its antecedent cells. 2. A mature male or female germ cell usually possessing a haploid chromosome set and capable of initiating formation of a new diploid individual by fusion with a gamete of the opposite sex.

Subject: brain commissure [PLANA:0000494]
Value: any of the nerve fiber tracts that span the longitudinal fissure between the cerebral and/or cerebellar hemispheres of the brain

Subject: testis somatic gonadal cell [PLANA:0004506]
Value: dmd-1+ expressing somatic cells within the testis that promote male GSC maintenance. dmd-1+, ophis-1+ somatic gonadal cells ensheath germ cells via long cytoplasmic processes and promote differentiation.

Subject: ovarian somatic gonadal cell [PLANA:0004507]
Value: ophis+ somatic cells (gh4-, nanos-) in the ovary that may provide trophic support to female germline stem cells and differentiating oogonia.

Subject: temporary embryonic pharynx epithelial cell [PLANA:0004521]
Value: foxA1+ epithelial cell contained in the temporary embryonic pharynx.

Subject: TrpA+ neural progenitor cell [PLANA:0007546]
Value: piwi-1+, runt-1+, ap2+ progenitor neoblasts required for production of TrpA+ neurons.

Subject: anterior pole progenitor cell [PLANA:0007547]
Value: piwi-1+, foxD+, prep+ progenitor neoblasts required for formation of the anterior pole.

Subject: serotonergic neural progenitor cell [PLANA:0007550]
Value: piwi-1+, lhx1/5-1+, pitx+ progenitor neoblasts required for specification of tph+ serotonergic neurons.

Subject: klf+ sensory neuron progenitor cell [PLANA:0007551]
Value: piwi-1+, klf+ progenitor neoblasts required for production of cintillo+ sensory neurons.

Subject: pax3/7+ neural progenitor cell [PLANA:0007555]
Value: piwi-1+, pax3/7+ progenitor neoblasts implicated in the production of DBH+ ventral midline neurons.
